race.description: Tabtouch Regional Championship - Road To Ascot
race.comment: Competitive. TWIST OF GOLD (3) keeps holding a strong level of form and went close here the latest in stronger grade. Won comfortably prior and she has the gate speed to use the inside barrier. Has a 3kg claimer aboard today and can bounce back. SCIENCE DEGREE (1) is a leader who won a 58 last time as expected. Keeps the handy 3kg claim and will prove hard to peg back again. EEVALINA (2) was a touch plainer last time but ran a big number beaten 1L in an Open 3 before that. Needs a good ride but has Faithful aboard today and can't be ruled out. DREAMERS NEVER DIE (4) is the third of the Peter Fernie acceptors and has a low gate and Fiore aboard for the first time. He showed enough last time to consider. PENNED (7) is also going well enough to consider.
